newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,282 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,282 contracts.

text.p: The Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 1,282 contracts compared with 1,449 overnight Tuesday.
There were 131 wheat, 448 corn, 594 soybean, 11 soymeal, 22 soyoil, four rice, four wheat puts, 33 soybean calls and 35 soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was steady to 1/2 cent lower, corn was steady to 1/4 lower and soybeans were one cent lower to 1-1/2 cents higher.
